cs.GT, cs.CE, cs.ET, cs.DS, cs.SI 

The paper deals with mechanism design, game theory, and optimization in the context of renewable energy aggregation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). The paper also involves computational economics (cs.CE), electronic commerce (cs.ET), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and social and information networks (cs.SI) as it discusses the design of a mechanism for aggregating renewable power producers in a two-settlement power market.
